				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Ba-n%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-moSMsl8t21K08pr2JOCm4Q">Ba nữ từ - 巴女詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BA%BFn-Hu%C3%A2n/Du-T%E1%BB%91ng-H%C6%B0ng-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-nham/poem-IRNXIDF8L5GPto1XuD_tEQ">Du Tống Hưng tự đông nham - 遊宋興寺東巖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BA%BFn-Hu%C3%A2n/author-pt0FwS8LzwRdBs25kowCsg">Lý Kiến Huân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Qu%C3%BD-%C6%AFng/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ng%C3%B4-Kh%C3%AA/poem-iBsWf2PnetTmh-EdYDn4Eg">Đề Ngô Khê - 題浯溪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Qu%C3%BD-%C6%AFng/author-KLfH9nbjfo3blYbVIGKyGA">Nguyễn Quý Ưng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Gi%C3%A1-c%C3%B4-thi%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n/poem-nZhhwxFvUgnIz139YF8EAg">Giá cô thiên - Tống nhân - 鷓鴣天－送人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%A1o-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-IpGv3JcIXGg0itJLhjmKgg">Hạo ca hành - 浩歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/Kh%C3%A1ch-x%C3%A1-ho%E1%BA%A1-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-VclkQwyypILOWJVLnWR_7g">Khách xá hoạ hữu nhân vận - 客舍和友人韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/M%C3%A3-%C3%8Dch-Chi-y%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-S%C6%A1n-%E1%BB%A9ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%E1%BA%A7n-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Dung-huy%E1%BB%87n-Du%E1%BA%ABn-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-kh%C3%A1n-hoa-nh%E1%BB%8B-c%C3%B4ng-t%C3%A1c/poem-5qmyVSmGwZ1HI7ELVbprxA">Mã Ích Chi yêu Trần Tử Sơn ứng phụng Tần Cảnh Dung huyện Duẫn giang thượng khán hoa, nhị công tác “Trúc chi ca”, dư diệc tác sổ thủ kỳ 07 - 馬益之邀陳子山應奉秦景容縣尹江上看花二公作竹枝歌予亦作數首其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-72N6ob4Hsg7Gc-KrAOsrTA">Viên Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Qu%C3%A1-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-phi-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-8BmXSWEqw0U_RMA2MXkEHA">Quá Tương phi miếu - 過湘妃廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-bi%E1%BA%BFm-Gi%C3%A1p-Trung-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-bi%E1%BA%BFm-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Sa/poem-WlSbS0D9s5mtpoEgdRajNw">Tống Lý thiếu phủ biếm Giáp Trung, Vương thiếu phủ biếm Trường Sa - 送李少府貶峽中王少府貶長沙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Th%C3%ADch/author-daTT9TQ-QJ39piO86WPo5Q">Cao Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-T%E1%BB%95ng/%C6%AF-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-quy-ho%C3%A0n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-c%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%C3%A0nh-Vi-S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%BA-%C3%A2m/poem-ftl85zOw6l1xa3XrBuni6w">Ư Trường An quy hoàn Dương Châu, cửu nguyệt cửu nhật hành Vi Sơn đình phú âm - 於長安歸還揚州，九月九日行薇山亭賦韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-T%E1%BB%95ng/author-xtvXUPvgiFTnJnow4yexuw">Giang Tổng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
